PIs of the SP: 
20-24 UT UHF (arc1(v2), cp1): T. Sakanoi and Y. Tanaka (March 24-30)
00-04 UT UHF (arc1(v2), cp1): Y. Ogawa (March 10 and 12)
00-04 UT UHF (arc1(v2), cp1): Y. Miyoshi and Y. Ogawa (March 24-31)
22-04 UT VHF (manda, zenith): Y. Miyoshi and K. Shiokawa (PP: COBEE)

We conduct coordinated observations of various auroras with ERG (Arase),
ground-based optical imagers, and EISCAT, to investigate small-scale aurora and
relativistic electron precipitations associated with pulsating aurora. 


